/PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/7/IST-OPEhotel_Other_4.jpg</Url><Width>360</Width><Height>240</Height><Bytes>0</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/7/IST-OPEhotel_Other_4_thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>80</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>60</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>0</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/7/IST-OPEhotel_Guest_Room_5.jpg</Url><Width>240</Width><Height>360</Height><Bytes>0</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/7/IST-OPEhotel_Guest_Room_5_thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>60</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>80</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>0</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>It is a new modern 4 star hotel combining the great location with a great roof top restaurant. In 1960s the building was a hotel where the american soldiers were staying and had been demolished in 1970s. Now it is in the same location with the same name from the beginning.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>The hotel is located in Gumussuyu Taksim which is just steps away to Taksim square and Kabatas Ferry Port. The hotel is just opposite to the Gulhane Military Hospital and Istanbul Technical University so it is a very secure area.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>Each room at Opera Hotel is decorated in a modern style. They all feature a seating area and minibar.  Even the rooms on the backyard of the hotel has a garden view which is very refreshing and hard to find in Taksim area.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>PropertyInformation</Type><Text>It is a modern building with a modern architecture. It is a new building which all the new high quality products used.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>The hotel has a roof top restaurant with a mix of international and turkish cuisine. . The interior design of the restaurant is fantastic and also sky dome ceiling has a breathtaking view of the bosphorus sea. These beauties makes this restaurant also a popular restaurant for local people.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>Short</Type><Text>The hotel has a huge lobby connecting with the lobby restaurant &amp; cafe. Plenty of seating capacity makes the hotel comfortable for the group arrivals.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Sauna</Code><Text>Sauna</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>BusinessCenter</Code><Text>Business center</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>OutdoorPool</Code><Text>Outdoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Gym</Code><Text>Fitness room / Gym</Text></Amenity><Rating><System>Stars</System><Score>40</Score><Description>Four star</Description></Rating><Rank>1</Rank></HotelElement>